" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dit1665703532527.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dit1665703532527.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dit1665703532527.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dit1665703532527\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ProcScript instruction clrmess\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determine whether the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span> ProcScript instruction is enabled.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dit1665703532527__section_w1439ab1b5b1_w1440ab1b5_w1441ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__1\">\n Representation\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__1\">\n Enabled\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__2\">Enable the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span>\n                        ProcScript statement in your ProcScript. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__1\">\n Disabled\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dit1665703532527__table_d18524e1_d18525e1_d18526e1__entry__2\">Disable the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span>\n                        ProcScript statement in your ProcScript. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dit1665703532527__section_ek5_d4h_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d273218e106\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dit1665703532527__p_d175868e1_d175869e1_d175870e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span> ProcScript statement\n            clears all messages from the application's message frame. During debugging, this is\n            usually undesirable, so the default is to disable it.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419468\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419468\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ProcScript instruction clrmess Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ProcScript instruction clrmess Determine whether the clrmess ProcScript instruction is enabled. Representation Description Enabled Enable the clrmess ProcScript statement in your ProcScript. Disabled Disable the clrmess ProcScript statement in your ProcScript. Description The clrmess ProcScript statement clears all messages from the application's message frame. During debugging, this is usually undesirable, so the default is to disable it. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}